@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_poogup(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin((tmp * (v0 + 0.67 + tmp + 0.48)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.27) / 0.16)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(v2))
    v0 = 0.81
    v1 = (0.49 - (0.92 + v0))
    tmp = (0.75 / wp.abs((v0 + 0.98 * tmp + 0.72)))
    tmp = (0.82 + ((tmp + 0.69 * v1 + 0.71) - 0.17))
    data[tid] = v0
